{"tid":1224074,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]新季Diablo2 美西專家拓荒區","createTime":"2019-06-15T01:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T19:01:30.000Z","uid":89287,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"32515dd1cb906bbaad7146c911e98c1bb92cace5","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"又係我開post<br />\n<br />\n新一季今日（8月16朝早8點正）開始 快d瘋狂打d2 hardcore<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加入既人都可以上返BATTLENET買KEY TOTAL應該大約150HKD 係有D貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為左避免大家前期花式自殺 簡單講下小弟玩左幾季既起手提示<br />\n1. 由A1慢慢行到A5 千其唔好急住要RUSH 因為所有人都係FRESH START 冇人可以100% CARRY你 而呢樣對你後期都好大幫助 因為你如果想人RUSH 我自己覺得行到A2尾+升到20-25LV係會令人想RUSH<br />\n2. 打到3洞盾要留 打到A2即刻解Q2救人任 拎古代人符文組 咁樣基本上NORMAL就唔會死好安全<br />\n3. 可以先玩法 打到裝再玩其它職 但我咁多季都係冰法起家 前前後後死過超過20隻80LV以上既角 先累積到經驗同技巧點樣冇咁易死 如果求安全 可以死靈起家 但後期相對上較悶 而共它職係冇傳送//迷團後期刷裝都好慢 所以最後都係靠你自己決定<br />\n4. 心態: 咩情況唔好衝 除非絕對安全 因為HARDCORE你得一條命 唔可以隨便揮霍 玩到HELL都見唔少人因為鳩衝而死 特別係係CHAOS 好彩既一日分分鐘見到5+既傻仔因為衝前根住比怪秒(我都做過) 你要知道係呢隻GAME入面好多意料之外既危險 <br />\n就算你爆抗 但冇防 比怪近攻會死<br />\n就算你爆防 但抗低 都好易比怪打到瀕血玩完<br />\n就算你爆防爆抗加有BOBO 4000+血 一樣可以比8人埸既DOLLS炸死 都可以比一堆8人埸既SOUL PACKS秒殺<br />\n所以無論玩到邊個STAGE都要好小心<br />\n<br />\n有興趣加入一齊玩: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GXAp0hV09Dk7yEvUZkC68Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGXAp0hV09Dk7yEvUZkC68Q&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlXwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=abf0f3a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GXAp0hV09Dk7yEvUZkC68Q</a><br />\n唔想入gp又要幫手係post出聲 盡幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係玩BOT既麻煩你地自己開過第二個GROUP玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39bsbK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39bsbK2.jpg&h=ef71e982&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b23453014bdf8c403d548151ae7c1980f9f4dee","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ab99784a968bf57775a226b9dff24aa445bac1","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4645504f6c2784f9180926e1bdc36909d57fe56a","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf86dcd4fc3fb3295d43c918b2b15e2d037402e","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b10fe87dc1903df9e58d3835b35fb220ad573e","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509f03587589c31d97b78152044e821f35d54665","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240876c36e360176947a63cb14de6d2f3c15e38c","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27697f835fd78290904da02b34ea00e8e2975b35","tid":1224074,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7859